data.description: Charming 3 bed 1.5 bath located in the Beautiful St. Clair Place neighborhood. The home features original Hardwood Floors, New Siding, Updated Bathrooms, New Vanity, New Roof, 3yr old Furnace/A/C /Water Heater, New Sewage/Water line, New Electric Wiring, 5yr old windows, and Much More!!!! Located just 5 mins from Downtown Indy, less than 5 mins from the Bottleworks community and next Door to Historical Woodruff Place makes this a perfect home for you in the metro area. The tenants are paying $2,200/month with lease agreement ending May 1, 2024.
